name: Shivam Family Restaurant

reviews.review_text: The crispy chicken and cheese garlic nan was a good combo. The staff behaviour is really good. The pricing is descent while comparing to other restaurants in Goa.

Though this restaurant is not that well known as other restaurants, this is one of the finest sea food restaurant in Goa.

The fish thali is outstanding. The service is impeccable. Ambience is good, not great though. But the food leaves a tangible taste in the tongue.

Will definitely visit many more times.

Highly recommended Fish Thali in Goa

The place is beautiful and on road so no confusion in finding the restaurant. The staff is very friendly and cooperative. Ordering is also easy. The fish thali contains a lot of dishes, affordable and all the dishes were tasty.
Overall it is a very great place to visit with your family.

description:
### Shivam Family Restaurant: A Hidden Gem in Goa

Nestled in the bustling streets of Goa, **Shivam Family Restaurant** has garnered an impressive **rating of 4.1** based on **843 reviews**. Renowned for its seafood offerings, particularly the popular **fish thali**, this dining establishment has become a compelling choice for both locals and visitors looking to indulge in the flavors of the sea. With additional highlights such as **prawns**, **curry**, and **rava fry**, it’s no wonder patrons consistently rave about their culinary experiences here.

#### Ambiance & Design

As you approach Shivam Family Restaurant, its convenient roadside location makes it easily accessible, preventing any confusion on your journey. The décor strikes a balance between simplicity and warmth, with tasteful adornments hinting at Goan culture. While reviews indicate that the ambiance could be enhanced, it still provides a comfortable setting for family dining. The photos capture inviting tables set against a backdrop of gentle lighting, creating a laid-back vibe perfect for relaxed meals. 

#### Menu & Culinary Experience

The heart of Shivam Family Restaurant lies within its diverse menu, showcasing an array of seafood delights, particularly the highly recommended **fish thali**. One reviewer describes it as "outstanding" and complete with several dishes that allow diners to explore Goan flavors at an affordable price. The thali is known not only for its generous portions but also for the delightful flavors that leave a lingering taste on the palate. Other noteworthy mentions include the **prawns**, crispy chicken, and **cheese garlic naan**, which are highlighted for their excellent pairing and taste. Culinary enthusiasts will appreciate the thoughtful presentation, making each dish not just a meal, but a feast for the senses.

#### Customer Experience & Service

Patrons consistently commend the **impeccable service** at Shivam Family Restaurant. Reviewers mention how the staff is notably **friendly and cooperative**, contributing to a family-friendly atmosphere that encourages guests to feel at home. The ordering process is described as straightforward, adding ease to the overall dining experience. While specific reservation or walk-in policies were not detailed, the welcoming nature of the staff suggests that patrons would be well taken care of regardless of their dining plans.

#### Popularity & Reviews

Despite being lesser-known than some of its competitors, Shivam Family Restaurant has carved out a niche for itself as one of the finest seafood establishments in the area. The positive sentiment shared among customers highlights the quality of food and conscientious service, making it a **highly recommended** spot for seafood lovers in Goa. Social media buzz around their **fish thali** has further enhanced its reputation, ensuring that many visitors plan multiple visits to savor its delights.

#### Utilizing Visual Content

The restaurant’s appeal is captured beautifully in customer-provided photos accompanying some reviews. Images showcase vibrant dishes that not only look enticing but exemplify the variety and quality that Shivam offers. From the colorful celebration of flavors in their fish thali to the cozy setting of the restaurant, these visuals serve as a testament to what diners can expect when they visit.

In essence, ***Shivam Family Restaurant*** stands out not just for its delectable food—especially for seafood aficionados—but also for its warm hospitality and inviting atmosphere. It proves to be an excellent choice for families seeking a memorable dining experience in Goa, with a promise of returning for more of what they do best: tantalizing seafood dishes crafted with care and passion.
